WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 14]

02:24.240 --> 02:25.410
What a pity.

02:28.150 --> 02:29.680
We were this close to finding the answer.

02:33.590 --> 02:34.660
The prayer ceremony

02:35.030 --> 02:36.130
begins now.

02:39.120 --> 02:40.220
Isn't the prayer ceremony

02:40.240 --> 02:41.930
supposed to be held two days before the wedding?

02:42.590 --> 02:43.220
Besides,

02:44.560 --> 02:46.340
I've already stolen the Radiant Moon.

02:48.120 --> 02:49.170
What's going on?

02:51.430 --> 02:52.570
People always say

02:53.560 --> 02:54.570
that the past can't be changed,

02:55.280 --> 02:56.410
and that years flow like water.

02:57.630 --> 02:58.730
This is the first time

02:59.080 --> 03:00.820
I've felt it so vividly.

03:01.800 --> 03:02.540
Humans

03:03.190 --> 03:04.130
and demons alike,

03:04.870 --> 03:06.220
even the Dragon Deity himself,

03:06.870 --> 03:08.120
are so small

03:08.910 --> 03:10.420
before fate.

03:11.190 --> 03:12.260
Inside the Star Stone

03:13.280 --> 03:14.630
is an illusion of the past.

03:15.190 --> 03:16.520
Since it's the past,

03:16.910 --> 03:18.340
it cannot be reversed

03:18.710 --> 03:19.340
or changed.

03:20.090 --> 03:20.820
The moment

03:20.840 --> 03:22.480
something that could alter the past happens,

03:23.430 --> 03:25.220
the illusion will shift and leap,

03:26.030 --> 03:26.820
correcting itself automatically

03:27.310 --> 03:28.610
to erase the traces of error

03:30.560 --> 03:31.690
and move on to the next

03:32.590 --> 03:34.340
destined moment that cannot be changed.

03:52.820 --> 03:54.730
You keep looking at me without saying anything.

03:55.520 --> 03:56.480
What do you want?

03:58.840 --> 03:59.690
If you'd known

04:00.750 --> 04:02.220
you couldn't use demon magic just now,

04:06.240 --> 04:07.220
would you still have stepped

04:07.240 --> 04:08.380
in front of me without hesitation?

04:12.310 --> 04:13.380
Of course not.

04:13.800 --> 04:14.540
I'm not stupid.

04:40.870 --> 04:41.730
What are you looking at?

04:43.740 --> 04:44.430
The moon.

04:48.600 --> 04:49.140
Don't be ridiculous.

04:50.430 --> 04:51.810
The sky is pitch-black.

04:52.120 --> 04:52.730
Where's the moon?

04:54.070 --> 04:54.540
It's there.

04:56.310 --> 04:57.250
It's called Hui.
[*new moon]

05:03.040 --> 05:03.780
I've heard

05:04.480 --> 05:06.090
that everyone in the Formless Moon

05:06.160 --> 05:07.660
has a mark on their arm.

05:08.390 --> 05:09.340
Why don't you have one?

05:11.430 --> 05:14.410
Because my moon phase is Hui.

05:15.600 --> 05:16.050
Hui?

05:16.630 --> 05:17.270
When you

05:17.270 --> 05:18.850
can't see the moon at night,

05:19.510 --> 05:20.490
that moon phase

05:21.600 --> 05:22.250
is Hui.

05:24.480 --> 05:25.370
You said

05:26.360 --> 05:27.950
that even if you were shattered to pieces,

05:28.160 --> 05:29.150
you could still be reborn.

05:30.430 --> 05:31.620
But will the reborn you

05:33.800 --> 05:34.890
still be the original you?

05:37.240 --> 05:39.170
The Primordial Sacred Spring can share

05:39.750 --> 05:40.810
and preserve memories.

05:41.630 --> 05:43.410
We are all reborn with memories.

05:43.850 --> 05:45.010
That's incredible.

05:47.190 --> 05:48.580
What does it feel like

05:50.120 --> 05:51.290
to share memories with others?

05:54.800 --> 05:56.250
It's hard to explain.

05:58.190 --> 05:58.900
Is it really?

06:03.160 --> 06:04.700
The Golden Scale Tree in the Shilin Sect

06:04.750 --> 06:06.470
has always had a special fragrance.

06:06.630 --> 06:07.350
You know that, right?

06:07.920 --> 06:08.340
Of course.

06:09.750 --> 06:10.660
Then how would you

06:10.680 --> 06:12.130
describe that scent to someone

06:12.190 --> 06:13.580
who's never been to the Shilin Sect?

06:18.750 --> 06:19.590
I think

06:21.630 --> 06:22.580
I understand what you mean now.

06:24.120 --> 06:25.140
Take

06:26.360 --> 06:27.650
the special scent you carry

06:27.650 --> 06:28.910
for example.

06:29.240 --> 06:30.530
I can't describe what it's like either.

06:31.390 --> 06:32.910
You've described it plenty of times,

06:33.950 --> 06:34.770
comparing it

06:35.630 --> 06:36.730
to wildflowers in a mountain valley

06:37.310 --> 06:38.170
and heavy snow at an ancient temple.

06:41.680 --> 06:42.930
Do I really carry a scent?

06:44.920 --> 06:45.730
You do.

06:46.270 --> 06:47.410
You always think I'm lying to you.

06:51.160 --> 06:52.660
Maybe it's just my natural scent.

07:01.180 --> 07:02.740
There's no new moon in the sky,

07:03.790 --> 07:05.230
just like I didn't exist in the Formless Moon either

07:06.600 --> 07:07.210
at the very start.

07:08.870 --> 07:10.300
When I was first born,

07:11.710 --> 07:12.860
I always dreamed

07:14.320 --> 07:15.090
that my sisters

07:15.160 --> 07:16.740
couldn't see me

07:17.630 --> 07:19.220
when I was with them.

07:22.580 --> 07:24.740
♪In the light, the great tree♪

07:25.100 --> 07:30.260
♪Sways gently, watching the mortal world burn bright♪

07:30.740 --> 07:32.140
♪Oh, little blade of grass♪

07:32.620 --> 07:36.940
♪I want to go somewhere else♪

07:37.860 --> 07:40.660
♪How do you measure memory♪

07:40.900 --> 07:45.740
♪To cut the past into clothes to wear?♪

07:45.860 --> 07:48.780
♪The little blade of grass, eyes brimming with tears♪

07:48.900 --> 07:53.540
♪Holds fallen leaves and grieves♪

07:54.620 --> 07:56.780
♪Summer heat fades into autumn's chill♪

07:56.860 --> 07:58.540
♪Winter snow falls in haste♪

07:58.660 --> 08:02.260
♪Then spring dew brings hope again♪

08:02.900 --> 08:04.100
♪Don't be afraid♪

08:04.540 --> 08:07.820
♪The passing years are nothing more than an evening glow♪

08:09.160 --> 08:09.780
Wangyan,

08:11.000 --> 08:11.850
thank you.

08:15.360 --> 08:16.810
You're the only one who can see me.

08:17.720 --> 08:19.540
You always hide in the dark.

08:20.360 --> 08:21.100
Of course the others

08:21.100 --> 08:22.450
can't see you easily.

08:24.440 --> 08:25.370
But I can.

08:26.720 --> 08:27.460
My heart

08:28.920 --> 08:30.490
can feel where you are.

08:32.600 --> 08:33.220
Later,

08:33.870 --> 08:35.800
Wangyan always took me with her wherever she went.

08:36.730 --> 08:37.940
And I never had

08:37.940 --> 08:39.240
those lonely dreams again.

08:40.790 --> 08:42.250
Though the new moon exists,

08:43.200 --> 08:44.650
barely anyone can see it.

08:47.630 --> 08:48.890
Only those who care about it

08:49.790 --> 08:51.010
will keep looking up

08:52.910 --> 08:54.770
and search for it in all that darkness.

08:58.840 --> 08:59.730
I can see it.

09:02.630 --> 09:04.370
Whether it's the waxing and waning moon

09:05.720 --> 09:06.980
or the stars spread across the sky,

09:08.550 --> 09:09.770
they all have their own orbits.

09:11.740 --> 09:12.720
No place

09:14.080 --> 09:14.980
can ever replace another.

09:21.200 --> 09:22.130
You're the Dragon Deity.

09:22.840 --> 09:23.770
Of course you wouldn't understand.

09:25.670 --> 09:26.890
But even the Dragon Deity will fall.

09:27.720 --> 09:29.010
My eight elder brothers

09:30.030 --> 09:30.890
are all gone.

09:32.750 --> 09:33.370
And one day,

09:34.720 --> 09:35.490
I will

09:37.600 --> 09:39.130
step down from this divine throne too.

09:42.840 --> 09:43.850
Are you afraid

09:45.750 --> 09:47.010
of falling,

09:48.790 --> 09:49.820
of no longer being a deity

09:49.840 --> 09:51.180
revered by all?

10:22.720 --> 10:23.340
Who would've thought?

10:25.240 --> 10:26.370
The stone we've been searching for

10:27.790 --> 10:28.580
is actually a person.

10:33.030 --> 10:34.210
But didn't the Star Stone

10:34.210 --> 10:36.270
shatter in that Meteor Blast long ago?

10:38.720 --> 10:39.680
Master Chi Wen,

10:41.320 --> 10:42.720
the Dragon Deity, saved me.

10:51.440 --> 10:53.060
I am disaster itself.

10:54.600 --> 10:55.820
I am the abyss.

10:58.030 --> 10:59.580
Why did you save me?

11:00.840 --> 11:02.420
If all it takes is one pebble falling

11:03.030 --> 11:03.980
to break the silence,

11:05.620 --> 11:07.340
then it is no longer an abyss.

11:09.270 --> 11:11.340
You bear extraordinary power from beyond the heavens.

11:11.790 --> 11:12.340
Slaughter

11:12.870 --> 11:14.420
is not your only choice.

11:16.000 --> 11:17.420
Now that your chains are gone,

11:17.870 --> 11:18.530
you are free.

11:19.270 --> 11:20.580
So is your will.

11:21.320 --> 11:22.100
It is up to you

11:22.630 --> 11:23.530
to choose

11:24.480 --> 11:25.610
between slaughter and protection.

11:27.320 --> 11:28.610
I hope that one day,

11:28.870 --> 11:31.290
you'll find the true meaning of coming to this world

11:31.600 --> 11:32.970
after crossing

11:33.270 --> 11:34.340
countless galaxies.

11:35.510 --> 11:37.300
Master Chi Wen even gave me a dragon fang

11:38.510 --> 11:40.060
and taught me how to control my power.

11:41.270 --> 11:42.850
But in the end, countless lives

11:42.870 --> 11:43.770
were still lost because of me.

11:44.600 --> 11:45.580
I couldn't forgive myself.

11:46.630 --> 11:47.580
After that,

11:47.960 --> 11:48.980
I became a monk

11:49.630 --> 11:50.530
and shaved my head.

11:51.340 --> 11:53.800
From that day on, there was no more Star Stone and no more Tian Di.

11:54.550 --> 11:56.190
Later, I wandered the mortal world,

11:56.630 --> 11:57.580
punishing the wicked.

11:58.360 --> 11:59.130
And before I knew it,

11:59.150 --> 12:00.620
I had earned myself a new fearsome name.

12:02.360 --> 12:04.140
No wonder people say

12:04.270 --> 12:05.910
you returned to worldly life, fell into demonhood,

12:06.240 --> 12:07.790
and became the demon monk

12:08.290 --> 12:09.610
known as Xie Lingxi.

12:11.150 --> 12:12.180
I was a demon to begin with.

12:12.960 --> 12:14.010
How could I "fall into demonhood"?

12:14.870 --> 12:16.130
I had no name in the first place.

12:16.720 --> 12:18.060
It makes little difference

12:19.550 --> 12:20.300
what the world calls me.

12:21.600 --> 12:22.980
But why did you come back here?

12:23.960 --> 12:25.700
Why do you refuse to help Wu Zhiqi

12:26.030 --> 12:27.770
lift the Petrification Curse from the Green Ape clan?

12:29.360 --> 12:30.460
You're tormenting him

12:32.360 --> 12:33.420
to take revenge on him, aren't you?

12:38.910 --> 12:40.700
I've never resented him.

12:42.550 --> 12:43.420
Why would I want revenge?

12:46.080 --> 12:46.700
I came back

12:47.670 --> 12:49.730
because of a promise I once made to Chi Wen.

12:51.240 --> 12:51.850
I promised him

12:55.320 --> 12:56.730
I would protect someone for him.

13:03.030 --> 13:03.580
So

13:06.960 --> 13:08.060
I've hated the wrong person all along.

13:09.390 --> 13:10.610
The slaughter of the flood dragon clan

13:11.670 --> 13:13.100
wasn't Shilin Sect or Chi Wen's doing...

13:35.440 --> 13:36.100
Iced lotus seeds?

13:37.600 --> 13:38.700
You can use demon magic again?

13:41.270 --> 13:42.650
I made them in my room

13:42.960 --> 13:43.900
after the prayer ceremony.

13:45.420 --> 13:46.480
When I was little,

13:47.000 --> 13:48.620
Wangyan used to make them for me all the time.

13:49.040 --> 13:50.160
They're crisp and refreshing.

13:53.960 --> 13:54.810
It feels

13:57.120 --> 13:58.530
like I've been apart from Wangyan forever.

14:03.240 --> 14:04.040
Go on. Try them.

14:04.670 --> 14:05.420
Once you've finished,

14:05.510 --> 14:06.700
we'll go get the Star Stone

14:07.030 --> 14:07.890
and get out of here.

14:15.630 --> 14:16.340
I forgot.

14:17.240 --> 14:18.220
Master Chi Wen

14:18.600 --> 14:20.250
never eats what others give him.

14:22.390 --> 14:23.340
I shouldn't have bothered...

14:43.000 --> 14:44.610
Sometimes I think

14:45.550 --> 14:47.460
about the real Di Zhu from over 1,000 years ago.

14:51.120 --> 14:51.730
Do you think

14:53.390 --> 14:54.490
she was foolish?

14:57.240 --> 14:59.820
People often say that love is a gamble,

15:00.600 --> 15:01.530
and that the heart is the stake.

15:04.600 --> 15:05.420
But some people

15:06.390 --> 15:07.990
will wager everything they have

15:09.030 --> 15:10.300
even when they're battered and bruised.

15:13.720 --> 15:15.060
But Di Zhu lost that gamble.

15:15.840 --> 15:16.980
In the legend, Man Man

15:17.240 --> 15:18.300
was a killer.

15:20.000 --> 15:20.940
But I think

15:22.120 --> 15:22.650
Man Man

15:23.390 --> 15:24.940
truly loved Di Zhu.

15:28.360 --> 15:29.700
Whether he did or not,

15:30.870 --> 15:32.460
Man Man still deceived Di Zhu.

15:34.670 --> 15:35.650
And I

15:37.240 --> 15:38.300
hate deception more than anything.

15:41.960 --> 15:44.370
Are you implying something?

15:55.850 --> 15:56.470
You...

16:34.150 --> 16:35.670
In the end, I still can't

16:36.670 --> 16:38.730
leave this Star Stone illusion, can I?

16:40.550 --> 16:41.530
A Star Stone illusion?

16:44.960 --> 16:45.820
You mean

16:47.550 --> 16:49.180
this is an illusion created by me?

16:57.670 --> 16:58.530
I understand now.

17:01.360 --> 17:02.250
In this illusion,

17:03.270 --> 17:05.300
there is a truth that you don't want him to know.

17:06.030 --> 17:07.710
So you want to kill the Star Stone

17:08.750 --> 17:10.140
and see whether that can break the illusion.

17:10.290 --> 17:12.920
My hands are already stained with blood.

17:15.310 --> 17:17.210
A little more won't matter.

17:21.480 --> 17:22.380
My weak point

17:23.350 --> 17:25.380
lies one cun below my left collarbone.

17:28.030 --> 17:28.420
Go on.

17:29.310 --> 17:30.000
Strike here.

17:35.150 --> 17:36.160
Why?

17:38.640 --> 17:39.250
Child,

17:40.400 --> 17:41.570
the shackles in your heart

17:43.070 --> 17:44.900
were not forged from your sins.

17:46.510 --> 17:47.330
Your heart

17:48.200 --> 17:50.220
has lost its way under pressure and self-torment.

17:51.270 --> 17:52.980
That's why I cannot see your heart.

17:54.480 --> 17:56.140
I'm willing to help free you from this sea of suffering.

17:57.750 --> 17:59.110
The splendor in a dream

18:00.400 --> 18:01.460
is, after all, illusory.

18:03.100 --> 18:05.900
♪You say don't look back♪

18:06.380 --> 18:08.660
♪Don't become like me♪

18:09.020 --> 18:10.940
♪Sands in the snow...♪

18:12.480 --> 18:13.490
Only when the dream ends

18:15.070 --> 18:16.180
does the truth appear.

18:19.640 --> 18:20.810
But the truth

18:22.440 --> 18:23.600
is too bitter.

18:30.400 --> 18:32.560
For the past millennium, I've been asking myself

18:34.750 --> 18:35.490
why

18:35.510 --> 18:37.070
I came into this world

18:39.180 --> 18:40.090
and what

18:42.400 --> 18:44.110
I could do for it.

18:59.550 --> 19:00.750
Master Chi Wen,

19:01.200 --> 19:02.170
you're finally awake.

19:03.570 --> 19:05.020
You were so well-behaved

19:05.350 --> 19:06.800
while you were asleep.

19:13.070 --> 19:14.940
You poisoned the iced lotus seeds?

19:16.880 --> 19:18.250
Don't make it sound so bad.

19:18.310 --> 19:19.400
It was only a sleeping draught.

19:20.350 --> 19:21.050
Still,

19:22.200 --> 19:24.460
getting you to lower your guard

19:24.920 --> 19:26.700
and obediently eat food from someone else

19:26.920 --> 19:28.180
was truly difficult.

19:28.510 --> 19:30.050
A fox really can't be trusted.

19:31.510 --> 19:32.620
What exactly are you trying to do?

19:35.270 --> 19:37.350
How can you sound so self-righteous

19:37.820 --> 19:39.540
when you were the one who played tricks first?

19:41.110 --> 19:41.710
Tell me.

19:42.510 --> 19:44.460
Why did you pour out the realgar powder from my sachet?

19:44.880 --> 19:46.380
Why are you dawdling? Come in.

19:47.290 --> 19:48.200
I'm coming.

19:59.000 --> 20:00.090
Are you that reluctant to leave?

20:02.270 --> 20:03.050
Don't tell me

20:03.720 --> 20:05.700
you really want to stay and marry me.

20:06.790 --> 20:07.960
Don't flatter yourself.

20:09.510 --> 20:11.050
I just want to catch the killer.

20:13.350 --> 20:14.570
Then I'm even more baffled.

20:15.400 --> 20:16.470
What's the point?

20:17.400 --> 20:19.010
This is an illusion of the past.

20:19.240 --> 20:20.620
None of this has anything to do with us.

20:21.400 --> 20:22.510
What happened in the past

20:22.640 --> 20:23.480
can't be undone

20:23.640 --> 20:24.410
or changed.

20:25.070 --> 20:26.420
So why go to all this extra trouble?

20:27.000 --> 20:28.420
Don't you think it's suspicious?

20:29.070 --> 20:30.220
A demon that can possess people

20:30.350 --> 20:31.620
and control them at will

20:32.240 --> 20:33.090
has always been

20:33.350 --> 20:34.220
exceedingly rare.

20:35.350 --> 20:35.940
Doesn't that

20:36.510 --> 20:37.700
remind you of anyone?

20:41.830 --> 20:42.660
Jiu Ying?

20:51.110 --> 20:52.730
You know the Star Stone better than anyone.

20:53.640 --> 20:54.940
Do the illusions inside it

20:55.480 --> 20:56.290
belong to anyone?

20:57.440 --> 20:58.420
Like dreams,

20:59.110 --> 21:00.710
whose memories are these illusions of the past

21:01.480 --> 21:02.550
they've entered?

21:03.960 --> 21:06.490
Among those who've entered the same illusion,

21:06.880 --> 21:08.290
one of them is

21:08.750 --> 21:10.150
the master of that illusion.

21:11.310 --> 21:13.140
It is a past they once lived through.

21:14.880 --> 21:16.380
But the wonder of the Star Stone

21:17.790 --> 21:19.220
is that the master's consciousness

21:20.310 --> 21:22.010
enters someone else's body

21:23.750 --> 21:25.330
to relive it all

21:27.000 --> 21:28.490
as an observer.

21:29.960 --> 21:30.460
That way,

21:31.240 --> 21:32.620
the things

21:32.720 --> 21:34.260
that have confused them for years

21:34.590 --> 21:36.950
can finally make sense when seen

21:37.440 --> 21:38.330
through an outsider's eyes.

21:39.270 --> 21:40.420
Take Wu Shiguang.

21:40.680 --> 21:41.740
He travelled

21:42.240 --> 21:44.660
to his own childhood.

21:45.400 --> 21:46.380
But he's

21:46.400 --> 21:47.510
reliving it

21:48.240 --> 21:49.660
through his father Cang Hao's perspective.

21:50.640 --> 21:51.930
So Wu Shiguang wants to find

21:52.830 --> 21:54.900
the truth behind the destruction of the flood dragon clan?

21:55.310 --> 21:55.700
No.

21:56.920 --> 21:59.110
It's the Star Stone that wants them to know the answers.

22:00.000 --> 22:00.860
The Star Stone?

22:01.110 --> 22:02.490
Didn't you see it too?

22:03.480 --> 22:04.570
It's Xie Lingxi.

22:05.720 --> 22:06.530
But

22:06.830 --> 22:08.180
the world Master Chi Wen

22:08.200 --> 22:09.010
and Lu Wuyi entered

22:09.030 --> 22:10.310
was from 1,000 years ago.

22:11.040 --> 22:12.900
It has nothing to do with either of them.

22:14.030 --> 22:15.570
Who is the master

22:17.790 --> 22:18.530
of that illusion?

22:20.350 --> 22:20.940
Bai Ze,

22:23.070 --> 22:24.380
why don't you ask me

22:25.680 --> 22:27.220
who the master is

22:27.960 --> 22:28.980
in Li Jie's illusion?

22:30.720 --> 22:31.730
So you do know.

22:33.200 --> 22:35.730
Who would've thought that Master Bai Ze, who knows everything under heaven,

22:37.110 --> 22:37.940
would have secrets too?

22:39.020 --> 22:40.310
Yuan Wuhuo.

22:42.000 --> 22:43.190
Yuan Xizai.

22:47.640 --> 22:48.490
How interesting.

22:52.310 --> 22:53.920
How did you find out where the Star Stone was hidden?

22:55.350 --> 22:57.370
Are there any other spies among the Green Ape clan?

22:58.420 --> 22:59.120
Report!

23:00.350 --> 23:01.170
Master Wu Zhiqi,

23:01.400 --> 23:02.550
Master Six-Eyed Butterfly has arrived.

23:02.680 --> 23:03.500
He's here to take the Star Stone.

23:04.030 --> 23:04.530
All right.

23:07.880 --> 23:09.980
This cage, like the chains on Tian Di,

23:10.920 --> 23:12.620
is made of tough spirit sand.

23:13.440 --> 23:15.090
Only the hardest obsidian

23:15.110 --> 23:15.900
can break it.

23:21.270 --> 23:22.140
You can't escape.

23:23.960 --> 23:24.940
And don't even think

23:25.720 --> 23:26.810
about taking Tian Di with you.

23:37.560 --> 23:38.540
You really shouldn't

23:38.560 --> 23:39.650
be trapped here by me.

23:41.640 --> 23:42.570
The world is vast,

23:44.160 --> 23:44.980
but it is cruel too.

23:46.840 --> 23:47.860
You can resent me

23:48.750 --> 23:49.610
or hate me,

23:51.070 --> 23:52.660
but some roads

23:56.720 --> 23:57.980
were destined for you and me all along.

24:20.310 --> 24:20.980
Don't be sad.

24:22.550 --> 24:23.620
He wants to let you go.

24:25.510 --> 24:26.420
Fortunately, the birthday gift

24:26.440 --> 24:27.620
my little brother gave me years ago

24:29.070 --> 24:30.290
was obsidian.

24:34.240 --> 24:36.290
Only the hardest obsidian

24:37.440 --> 24:38.290
can break it.

24:39.350 --> 24:40.330
Wu Zhiqi was

24:42.000 --> 24:43.860
reminding us on purpose.

25:11.270 --> 25:12.140
Good for you, Man Man.

25:13.270 --> 25:14.620
You knew where the Star Stone was

25:15.110 --> 25:16.090
and didn't tell me?

25:16.680 --> 25:18.180
The Star Stone isn't yours.

25:18.510 --> 25:19.460
Why should he tell you?

25:20.590 --> 25:22.010
You look human enough.

25:22.790 --> 25:23.490
Have you no shame?

25:25.270 --> 25:27.250
I knew something was off with you.

25:28.510 --> 25:29.660
Turns out you really did betray me.

25:30.440 --> 25:32.330
This woman is clearly pure trouble.

25:33.240 --> 25:34.180
A vixen through and through.

25:36.160 --> 25:37.220
Then do you know

25:38.000 --> 25:39.900
that foxes never forget a grudge?

25:40.880 --> 25:42.140
I still haven't settled the score

25:42.310 --> 25:43.420
for you killing me.

25:44.510 --> 25:45.290
Killing you?

25:46.200 --> 25:47.220
What do you mean, killing you?

25:48.030 --> 25:49.530
I'll kill you now!

26:16.440 --> 26:16.900
You...

26:19.200 --> 26:20.330
You're only human.

26:21.510 --> 26:22.850
Why are you immune to my magic?

26:29.590 --> 26:30.690
Looks like Lu Wuyi

26:30.690 --> 26:32.670
is even more formidable than we thought.

26:32.850 --> 26:33.640
Bai Ze,

26:34.240 --> 26:35.530
you know the secrets of all demons.

26:37.200 --> 26:38.700
What kind of power is this?

26:39.640 --> 26:41.030
The more she's attacked

26:41.030 --> 26:41.960
by the same kind of magic,

26:42.440 --> 26:43.250
the more she's able

26:43.310 --> 26:44.940
to absorb its power and grow immune to it.

26:54.110 --> 26:56.010
I've been away from the world too long.

26:57.030 --> 26:58.010
When did the people

26:58.510 --> 26:59.940
of the Formless Moon become this powerful?

27:01.920 --> 27:02.460
Be careful.

27:02.720 --> 27:03.660
What are you scared of?

27:05.940 --> 27:07.380
You killed me last time.

27:08.300 --> 27:11.130
Now it's time you paid back that life.

27:12.040 --> 27:13.210
What nonsense.

27:14.470 --> 27:15.780
I have no idea what you're talking about.

27:18.070 --> 27:19.050
Hand over the Star Stone.

27:19.240 --> 27:19.770
Don't act rashly.

27:20.350 --> 27:21.420
Give me the Star Stone,

27:22.510 --> 27:24.270
or I'll kill her right now.

27:24.270 --> 27:25.560
I was telling her not to act rashly.

27:29.720 --> 27:31.090
Kneel and obey me.

27:38.000 --> 27:39.250
Don't kill him. The illusion will go haywire!

28:20.020 --> 28:24.460
[The day of the Hurricane Catastrophe]

28:25.400 --> 28:26.490
I'll cut his chains.

28:26.750 --> 28:27.860
You go outside the cave first

28:28.350 --> 28:29.290
and see if there are any Green Ape guards.

28:29.750 --> 28:30.180
All right.

29:29.540 --> 29:31.540
[An hour before the Meteor Blast]

29:33.460 --> 29:35.180
A moth will fly

29:35.750 --> 29:37.060
into the flame

29:37.750 --> 29:39.310
even knowing it's wrong.

29:40.270 --> 29:40.980
I

29:42.110 --> 29:43.570
am no different.

30:00.270 --> 30:00.810
Master!

30:05.550 --> 30:06.090
Why?

30:13.070 --> 30:14.380
All things flourish and fade in their time.

30:15.720 --> 30:17.350
Life and death are nothing strange.

30:22.070 --> 30:23.490
I had hoped to see you through this,

30:25.070 --> 30:26.050
but it seems...

30:35.030 --> 30:35.750
Master...

30:37.030 --> 30:37.610
Master!

31:08.740 --> 31:14.300
[The day of the Great Freeze]

31:18.660 --> 31:20.060
What happened?

31:22.550 --> 31:24.250
The illusion seems to be jumping on its own.

31:25.830 --> 31:27.010
It's correcting itself automatically.

31:35.270 --> 31:36.770
Move that one over there.

31:36.880 --> 31:38.380
Time's jumped that far ahead?

31:50.350 --> 31:51.010
Di Zhu,

31:51.830 --> 31:52.960
here's the Star Stone!

31:56.750 --> 31:57.490
That's easy.

32:09.390 --> 32:10.650
What's going on?

32:13.040 --> 32:14.340
How did everything suddenly change?

32:17.280 --> 32:18.080
I don't know either.

32:25.720 --> 32:26.860
You're finally here.

32:35.110 --> 32:36.050
You've done well

32:36.400 --> 32:37.380
with the task we assigned you.

32:37.960 --> 32:38.570
Hand him over.

32:38.750 --> 32:39.700
I'll take him back to the Shilin Sect.

32:43.000 --> 32:44.620
The Shilin Sect will take good care of you.

32:45.550 --> 32:46.620
I'll go see you later.

32:57.350 --> 32:58.010
What are you doing?

32:59.240 --> 33:00.620
There's something hidden inside you.

33:01.270 --> 33:02.140
I'll help you take it out.

33:15.190 --> 33:17.390
Wu Shiguang is in my hands now.

33:19.640 --> 33:20.490
So it really was him.

33:25.720 --> 33:27.220
If you want him safe,

33:28.220 --> 33:30.630
lift the Petrification Curse from my clansmen.

33:38.820 --> 33:39.850
Master...

33:55.350 --> 33:56.810
Shiguang always calls you Master,

33:58.400 --> 33:59.380
but in his heart,

34:05.350 --> 34:06.980
he's always seen you as family.

34:10.160 --> 34:11.180
You're no child anymore.

34:12.800 --> 34:14.380
Why are you suddenly crying

34:14.400 --> 34:15.130
like one?

34:16.740 --> 34:17.300
♪So...♪

34:18.230 --> 34:18.820
Don't worry.

34:20.400 --> 34:21.690
I'll get Shiguang out.

34:24.740 --> 34:30.660
♪You are spring rain, your breeze drifting into my heart♪

34:31.820 --> 34:37.740
♪You are a rising tide, bringing a melody of highs and lows♪

34:38.820 --> 34:45.020
♪All my troubles are forgotten here♪

34:45.540 --> 34:51.860
♪Only you and I remain in our tiny world♪

34:53.020 --> 34:58.860
♪If you're a little boat, I'll be the shore♪

35:00.020 --> 35:06.020
♪Holding your weariness and all your joys and sorrows♪

35:07.060 --> 35:13.100
♪I truly cherish the sweetness in your smile♪

35:13.700 --> 35:19.620
♪So don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

35:21.260 --> 35:27.180
♪If you're the moon, I'll be falling snow♪

35:28.340 --> 35:35.020
♪Let them chase the skies, I'll stay with you below♪

35:35.340 --> 35:41.180
♪I truly miss the taste of your tears♪

35:41.420 --> 35:42.060
♪So please♪

35:42.380 --> 35:48.380
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

35:48.580 --> 35:49.180
♪So please♪

35:49.460 --> 35:55.060
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

35:55.660 --> 35:56.300
♪So please♪

35:56.500 --> 36:06.340
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

36:12.480 --> 36:14.260
So Master went to save me.

36:16.030 --> 36:16.830
If he hadn't gone

36:16.830 --> 36:18.780
with Wu Zhiqi that day,

36:21.230 --> 36:22.460
would everything have been different?

36:28.920 --> 36:29.530
Today

36:32.110 --> 36:33.490
is the day the flood dragon clan

36:35.510 --> 36:36.810
is wiped out.

36:51.150 --> 36:53.090
They're getting married!

36:54.030 --> 36:55.340
They're getting married!

36:57.360 --> 36:58.050
They're getting married!

36:59.800 --> 37:01.010
They're getting married!

37:07.280 --> 37:08.090
So this isn't a dream.

37:08.800 --> 37:10.240
Why didn't you pinch yourself?

37:10.590 --> 37:11.820
Because I'm not stupid.

37:11.900 --> 37:12.380
I...

37:14.670 --> 37:15.420
You know,

37:15.840 --> 37:17.980
that wedding robe looks good

37:18.400 --> 37:19.780
on you, Master Dragon Deity.

37:24.030 --> 37:24.900
A true dragon

37:25.280 --> 37:26.210
looks good in anything.

37:26.800 --> 37:27.490
No need to be surprised.

37:31.470 --> 37:33.820
A Dragon Deity above mortal concerns

37:34.360 --> 37:35.940
is suddenly decked out in gold and silver,

37:36.150 --> 37:37.170
about to wed.

37:37.510 --> 37:38.580
How's that not surprising?

37:43.000 --> 37:44.740
By the way, Master Dragon Deity,

37:45.440 --> 37:47.050
do you have any experience

37:47.510 --> 37:48.380
with the wedding night?

37:50.440 --> 37:52.010
Nothing unexpected will happen, right?

37:57.190 --> 37:57.650
Wait for me.

37:58.960 --> 37:59.510
Just wait here.

38:12.030 --> 38:14.380
I'm not getting jilted, am I?

38:33.710 --> 38:34.460
What is it?

38:36.630 --> 38:37.260
Something good.

39:01.420 --> 39:02.530
Trust me.

39:03.800 --> 39:05.780
This guarantees nothing can go wrong.

39:13.110 --> 39:13.900
Why are you smiling?

39:15.110 --> 39:15.900
You smiled first.

39:16.590 --> 39:17.210
No, you smiled first.

39:17.550 --> 39:18.260
You did first.

39:18.690 --> 39:19.670
You did first.

39:23.030 --> 39:23.530
I did first.

39:38.230 --> 39:39.820
If you make me fall, you're dead.

39:52.280 --> 39:53.980
By Sacred Heaven above,

39:54.480 --> 39:56.770
first bow to heaven and earth!

40:05.110 --> 40:06.300
- With the ancestors as witness... - Wonderful!

40:06.880 --> 40:08.050
Second bow to your kin!

40:17.190 --> 40:18.820
Let the holy mountain bear witness

40:19.230 --> 40:20.980
and the sacred waters seal your vow.

40:21.480 --> 40:23.380
Third bow to each other!

40:32.070 --> 40:32.820
I'm fine.

40:34.960 --> 40:36.820
Ceremony complete.

40:37.150 --> 40:37.900
Now kiss!

40:56.260 --> 40:59.820
♪If there's a little village down the road♪

41:00.420 --> 41:02.620
♪By a river bending soft and slow♪

41:03.060 --> 41:08.260
♪You hum a tune by the fire's glow♪

41:08.940 --> 41:12.300
♪Time would linger, never go♪

41:12.540 --> 41:17.580
♪Even the wind would fade, just you and me♪

41:17.780 --> 41:20.940
♪Hand in hand, we'd sit close, quietly♪

41:36.400 --> 41:36.900
Di Zhu,

41:38.480 --> 41:39.380
here's the Star Stone.

41:43.590 --> 41:44.380
Come out, Little Nine.

42:06.320 --> 42:06.820
Hold your breath.

42:07.440 --> 42:08.260
There's sleeping powder in the sandstorm.

42:50.960 --> 42:51.900
The Star Stone.

43:01.580 --> 43:02.740
♪It's your light♪

43:02.940 --> 43:04.820
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:04.980 --> 43:08.100
♪That set the night alight♪

43:08.460 --> 43:14.980
♪And lead me through the fight♪

43:16.740 --> 43:18.620
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

43:19.060 --> 43:23.500
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

43:24.300 --> 43:25.980
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

43:26.140 --> 43:31.540
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

43:32.300 --> 43:37.700
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

43:40.020 --> 43:46.060
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

43:47.020 --> 43:49.180
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

43:49.460 --> 43:54.300
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

43:54.660 --> 43:56.980
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

43:57.180 --> 44:02.260
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

44:02.500 --> 44:04.500
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

44:04.780 --> 44:09.140
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

44:10.140 --> 44:17.100
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

44:33.660 --> 44:36.620
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

44:37.700 --> 44:41.100
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

44:41.900 --> 44:44.420
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

44:44.660 --> 44:47.740
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

44:48.140 --> 44:50.460
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

44:50.980 --> 44:55.380
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

44:55.620 --> 44:57.780
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

44:58.180 --> 45:03.140
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

45:03.380 --> 45:04.540
♪It's your light♪

45:04.740 --> 45:06.580
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

45:06.780 --> 45:09.900
♪That set the night alight♪

45:10.660 --> 45:20.100
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
